title: Ann Coulter Booed, Makes 9/11 Quip at L.A.'s Politicon

Ann Coulter Booed, Makes 9/11 Quip at... Ann Coulter Booed, Makes 9/11 Quip at L.A.'s Politicon Next Story Prev Story 14 hrs ago Read more: Hollywood Reporter 
The conservative pundit was heckled by audience members during the inaugural two-day event Saturday at the Los Angeles Convention Center. The outspoken conservative pundit and best-selling author was interviewed by political commentator Cenk Uygur on Saturday at the inaugural Uygur is the progressive host of The Young Turks , a popular online news show covering an array of topics, including politics, economics and social trends.   Hollywood Reporter.
